'''Spinner''' is a term used primarily in the [[pornographic movie|adult film]] industry, but has also gained a small amount of mainstream use.

It refers to an actress with a tiny frame, usually very thin and having small breasts. Such a woman is so small that she can supposedly mount a man's penis and easily spin around on it. Two prominent examples of "spinners" in the porn industry are [[Ginger Lynn]] and [[Nikki Charm]].

The term has also been used to refer to an adult website which rotates ("spins") its content automatically and regularly, or which performs some advanced content matching to assist visitors in finding exactly what they are seeking.  

